com.worizon.jsonrpc

Class Const

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.worizon.jsonrpc.Const

  • public final class Const
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants for JSON-RPC low level code errors. The error object contains two fields: code and message. JSON-RPC 2.0 spec has several code numbers reserved to signal different transport errors and server implementations which honors JSONRPC 2.0 spec must use these error codes.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Enric Cecilla
    See Also:
    JSONRPC 2.0 error codes
